summary: Validate ownership and permissions of files in the image
description: |
  Builds an AIB image with custom ownership and permission settings
  and verifies that files in both content and QM paths have the expected values.

  Test inputs:
    Custom a-i-b manifest, which defines permissions and ownerships of files and directories, which should be added
    to the image created in the test.

  Expected results:
    - PASS: 'All file permissions and ownerships are correctly set.'

  Results location:
    output.txt

test:
    ./test-chown-chmod.sh
duration: 30m
